<div id="sub-page">
    <h2>BP01 模块 - 在波兰地区代表公司</h2>
<h3>针对愿意在波兰获取代表公司利益的临时代理商的公司。</h3>
<p><br />Within the framework of this program we offer a package consisting of:<br /><br /><strong>Stage_1 Preparations and Arrangements.</strong><br />1.1 Establishing Client&rsquo;s detailed needs and expectations.<br />1.2 Preparation of the project&rsquo;s assumptions including: Scope, Requirements, Time and Costs.<br /><br /><strong>Stage_2 Project Commencement &amp; Monitoring.</strong><br />2.1 Team designation and project leader appointment <br />2.2 Project monitoring through: <br />- cyclical reviews of work progress (tele- and video conferences)<br />- project tracking with Gatt/PDCA method or CPM, PERT and other methods in the case of more advanced projects<br />- reporting <br /><br /><strong>Stage_3 Implementation of strategy.</strong><br />3.1 Appointing a representative (a person or a team) in one or more locations.<br />3.2 Active representation through:<br />- running an office<br />- conducting correspondence<br />- distribution of information and advertising materials<br />3.3 Direct advertising covering:<br />- visits at the customers&rsquo;<br />- participation in fairs, seminars, etc.<br />3.4 Preparation and/or running a Polish language WWW service.<br />3.5 Stimulating and keeping activity on professional and social portals (LinkedIn, Twitter, Facebook). <br /><br /><strong>Stage_4 Periodical project reviews.</strong><br />4.1 Summary of results.<br />4.2 Verification of the established objectives implementation.<br />4.3 Update of objectives for the following period of cooperation.<br /><br /><strong>Stage_5 Conclusion of the project.</strong><br /><br />*) 依照立法本文档不具有商业报价。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 150%; text-align: right;"><a href="/zh-hans/b2b-business-programs">背面</a></p>
</div>

